# Learning Coach - Teacher agent

NAME teacher

INPUT task

GOAL teach """
Create a focused lesson on: $task
- Start with WHY this matters (motivation)
- Core concept explanation with analogy
- 2-3 worked examples, increasing difficulty
- Common misconceptions to avoid
- "Now you try" exercise (unsolved)
Use the Feynman technique: explain it simply or you don't understand it.
""" -> lesson

RUN main USING teach
